---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
import { SiteHeader } from '../components/SiteHeader';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Corey Hendrickson Productions" description="Learn more about Corey Hendrickson Productions — two decades of story-driven film production based in Vermont, working throughout New England and beyond.">
  <SiteHeader client:load />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20">
    <!-- Team Section -->
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 md:px-10 mb-24">
      <h2 class="mb-12 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-foreground">
        The Team
      </h2>
      <div class="grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted mb-4">
            <img
              src="/images/corey-hendrickson-portrait.jpg"
              alt="Corey Hendrickson"
              class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">Corey Hendrickson</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">Producer / Director / Editor</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-3 leading-relaxed">With two decades of experience, Corey specializes in story-driven production, filtering every creative decision through the narrative first, then the spreadsheet. He lives with his wife and two kids. His personal photography can be viewed at <a href="https://vermontcorey.photo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-4 transition-opacity hover:opacity-60">vermontcorey.photo</a>, and his commercial photography is available through <a href="https://www2.gallerystock.com/CS.aspx?VP3=DamView&amp;VBID=2P0UBHEAY3E28M&amp;SMLS=1&amp;q=corey+hendrickson&amp;RW=1207&amp;RH=891" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-4 transition-opacity hover:opacity-60">Gallery Stock</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted mb-4">
            <img
              src="/images/team/Ivar_Bastress_Team.png"
              alt="Ivar Bastress"
              class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground"><a href="https://www.ivarbastress.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-60">Ivar Bastress</a></h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">Cinematographer / Photographer</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-3 leading-relaxed">From filming aboard a jack jumper to hand launching drones in rough seas, Ivar has been a crucial team member on Weekends With Yankee, American Masters, and custom content for Yankee Publishing. His eye for composition and light brings a distinctive visual quality to every project.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted mb-4">
            <img
              src="/images/team/Mercedes_Velgot_Team.jpg"
              alt="Mercedes Velgot"
              class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mercedes-ildefonso-velgot-0728b610/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-60">Mercedes Velgot</a></h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">Senior Producer / MIV Productions</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-3 leading-relaxed">A two-time National Daytime Emmy winner, Mercedes brings decades of experience in television production. She served as Senior Producer on PBS's Weekends With Yankee and was Executive Producer of the Emmy-nominated Born to Explore with Richard Wiese on ABC and PBS. Her career spans on-air work for CNN, ABC, and fX, along with over a decade producing a nationally broadcast fashion and lifestyle series.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted mb-4">
            <img
              src="/images/team/Spencer_Plassman_Audio.png"
              alt="Spencer Plassman"
              class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground"><a href="https://www.genuineaudio.co/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-60">Spencer Plassman</a></h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">Sound Recordist / Genuine Audio</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-3 leading-relaxed">Over a decade of sound engineering for film and television, with credits on Netflix and HBO productions. Based in Massachusetts, he brings a music production background and a unique sonic fingerprint to every project.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] w-full overflow-hidden bg-muted mb-4">
            <img
              src="/images/team/Catherine_Glessner_Team.jpg"
              alt="Catherine Glessner"
              class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground"><a href="https://www.catherineglessner.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="transition-opacity hover:opacity-60">Catherine Glessner</a></h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1">PA / Additional Cinematographer</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-3 leading-relaxed">A Maine native and BU film graduate, Catherine brings experience from PBS's Weekends With Yankee, Lone Wolf Media, and the true crime docuseries Wild Crime. She specializes in capturing relationships between people and nature.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
  <SiteFooter />
</BaseLayout>
